    "The size of the adapted dataset is notably tiny, which could result in the risk of overfitting with less generalisation.",
    "However, our proposal has demonstrated improved performance in dealing with these issues due to the models learning a wide range of relevant features, which can be shown from the results considering S3 and S4.",
    "Three orthopaedic surgeons from Greenslopes Private Hospital-Brisbine Australia were invited to classify the test set for the MURA dataset-shoulder task.",
